00:28:46.504 --> 00:28:51.819
I believe you all say these things,

00:28:56.182 --> 00:28:58.182
and you listen to it,

00:29:08.173 --> 00:29:10.173
and you say it from your heart.

00:29:13.353 --> 00:29:19.577
Only the one who are united with God can worship Shri Ganesha.

00:29:23.824 --> 00:29:25.824
And Shri Ganesha worships your Mother.

00:29:40.414 --> 00:29:42.414
First of all

00:29:44.325 --> 00:29:46.325
one must to understand

00:29:48.941 --> 00:29:51.938
that there is a combination of a Mother and a Guru.

00:29:55.388 --> 00:29:57.388
Because Guru is a very hard task master.

00:30:00.164 --> 00:30:02.164
He does not allow any liberties to be taken.

00:30:05.229 --> 00:30:07.229
And Mother is very kindly.

00:30:13.628 --> 00:30:17.149
But you don't have feelings for the Mother, do you?

00:30:30.859 --> 00:30:33.685
Is it all a lip-service that you listen,

00:30:34.185 --> 00:30:37.696
goes into your head, and you think you have become

00:30:39.414 --> 00:30:41.774
the surrendered Sahaja yogis?

00:30:43.268 --> 00:30:47.175
Like all Islam people believe they are surrendered to God,

00:30:47.226 --> 00:30:50.226
like Christians believe they are surrendered to God.

00:30:51.560 --> 00:30:55.007
It's just a lip-service that you are this, you are that.

00:30:55.986 --> 00:31:00.762
Or do you know it him, what is said, is a fact.

00:31:04.340 --> 00:31:06.599
Have you not seen the Sun in my hand?

00:31:07.772 --> 00:31:09.421
What more proof you want?

00:31:31.456 --> 00:31:36.070
Anybody who misleads you is of course sinful no doubt,

00:31:38.313 --> 00:31:40.728
but to fall a trap to such a person!

00:31:43.939 --> 00:31:48.151
If you had told a child that the Mother is coming, he would have fought,

00:31:48.651 --> 00:31:49.438
"I'm going".

00:31:52.898 --> 00:31:54.898
He would have cried and wept.

00:31:59.880 --> 00:32:01.880
What about your vibrations?

00:32:03.099 --> 00:32:05.099
You don't use your vibrations?

00:32:06.844 --> 00:32:09.674
You have come all the way for Guru Puja here,

00:32:10.285 --> 00:32:13.047
who is your Guru? Whom are you going to worship?

00:32:14.681 --> 00:32:19.121
Anybody comes from anywhere becomes suddenly important. How?

00:32:26.344 --> 00:32:28.344
It was never done before,

00:32:29.231 --> 00:32:31.898
first time I see such a horrible thing.

00:32:34.418 --> 00:32:38.349
In my living time if you are doing like this, after my death so many gurus will rise,

00:32:39.306 --> 00:32:39.991
to mislead you.

00:32:48.293 --> 00:32:50.293
Are you going to accept all that?

00:33:09.911 --> 00:33:14.631
All the Deities refused for me to do this.

00:33:14.827 --> 00:33:18.386
They tortured my life, they would not accept

00:33:19.444 --> 00:33:24.043
to allow you to have the Puja. Absolutely, nothing doing.

00:33:28.997 --> 00:33:31.588
Because they love me, they respect me.

00:33:32.088 --> 00:33:34.088
They have the proper protocol.

00:33:34.145 --> 00:33:36.145
They don't want to become gurus themselves,

00:33:36.645 --> 00:33:38.645
and misbehave in this manner.

00:33:54.860 --> 00:34:01.045
Last time when I came I really was very strong, with the French.

00:34:04.339 --> 00:34:10.469
I've told so many times that France is the Hell of the Universe.

00:34:17.443 --> 00:34:21.369
And you should fall a trap to something like that?

00:34:21.980 --> 00:34:26.111
It's very supra-conscious, extremely supra-conscious.

00:34:27.648 --> 00:34:28.666
And arrogant.

00:34:39.901 --> 00:34:43.801
I've never known of such a Guru Puja. Never.

00:34:45.352 --> 00:34:48.499
Indians had only one Guru Puja, and they are praying that

00:34:48.805 --> 00:34:51.586
they should have at least one more Guru Puja.

00:34:52.916 --> 00:34:56.484
With all these Guru Pujas if you have achieved this kind of surrendering,

00:34:57.039 --> 00:34:59.775
it's better you do not have any more Guru Pujas at all.

00:35:00.275 --> 00:35:03.058
Don't deserve it. You cannot become Gurus,

00:35:03.558 --> 00:35:04.828
I can see that clearly.

00:35:06.324 --> 00:35:08.324
Without surrender how will you?

00:35:42.468 --> 00:35:45.835
All the Blessings of the Divine

00:35:47.774 --> 00:35:49.000
have been showered upon you.

00:35:51.796 --> 00:35:53.796
And what have you given back?

00:35:59.691 --> 00:36:01.691
Such ego?

00:36:02.191 --> 00:36:05.442
That you act to somebody because he has greater egos?

00:36:25.115 --> 00:36:27.115
It is a very bad example.

00:36:34.200 --> 00:36:37.935
You have to wash the feet of the Indians and drink that water.

00:36:38.435 --> 00:36:41.563
May be then you might realize where you are.

00:36:42.257 --> 00:36:44.257
You may be very developed and all that.

00:36:45.476 --> 00:36:47.476
And the Indians who are of your type,

00:36:49.055 --> 00:36:51.055
all of them have to do that.

00:36:59.108 --> 00:37:01.108
Why didn't you see your vibrations?

00:37:03.932 --> 00:37:07.752
When the blind gets his eyes, he doesn't close his eyes to see things, does he?

00:37:12.402 --> 00:37:14.402
And what has happened to your leaders also?

00:37:22.943 --> 00:37:24.943
All of them put together could not

00:37:25.015 --> 00:37:27.443
say that we will not have this nonsense at this time?

00:37:38.446 --> 00:37:42.604
Just coming to the airport, so many people have risen higher in life.

00:37:43.599 --> 00:37:44.834
What are you doing here?

00:37:51.433 --> 00:37:53.433
You should have protested.

00:37:56.335 --> 00:37:59.961
I would like to know how many wanted to go to the airport and asked for it.

00:38:00.061 --> 00:38:02.181
Raise your hands. Honestly.

00:38:05.271 --> 00:38:06.138
Honestly.

00:38:18.082 --> 00:38:20.082
These are the only people who love me.

00:38:24.322 --> 00:38:25.208
May God Bless you.

00:38:45.813 --> 00:38:48.897
Tomorrow somebody tells you to insult me, will you do that?

00:39:00.087 --> 00:39:04.471
You know that if a king arrives from a small little place somewhere,

00:39:06.196 --> 00:39:09.555
or a prime minister from a very small island,

00:39:14.374 --> 00:39:16.506
from lardy and muddy island

00:39:17.006 --> 00:39:18.208
the prime minister came,

00:39:19.022 --> 00:39:22.811
and the prime minister of England had to go receive him.

00:39:32.081 --> 00:39:33.728
And if your Guru has come,

00:39:33.831 --> 00:39:35.831
all the gurus have to come to receive me,

00:39:38.433 --> 00:39:40.583
or to listen to something nonsensical here?

00:39:44.690 --> 00:39:47.750
I felt like going back from the airport only,

00:39:48.250 --> 00:39:50.250
the kind of vibrations I felt.

00:39:55.847 --> 00:39:57.847
How do you get into this kind of a maya?

00:40:02.087 --> 00:40:05.250
How you join hands? Except for a few.

00:40:15.315 --> 00:40:17.315
“Your quality will be known:

00:40:19.321 --> 00:40:22.050
how much you are surrendered to Me".

00:40:23.344 --> 00:40:24.456
Christ has said that.

00:40:30.003 --> 00:40:31.734
And today I say to you that.

00:40:35.395 --> 00:40:37.962
On all other things Sahaja yogis will protest.

00:40:39.025 --> 00:40:41.855
"This was not good, that was not good, this was done”.

00:40:41.973 --> 00:40:44.421
Against each other, against everything they will protest.

00:40:50.663 --> 00:40:52.998
"Sahaja yogi took this much money from us, and

00:40:53.035 --> 00:40:55.035
