01:01:28.070 --> 01:01:29.277
the one who wanted this,

01:01:33.195 --> 01:01:36.346
Rolls Royce. They starved themselves for one year,

01:01:37.110 --> 01:01:38.442
bought a Rolls Royce,

01:01:43.770 --> 01:01:46.475
and went to receive him, and such a crowd

01:01:46.482 --> 01:01:48.711
that people could not get to the airport.

01:01:49.528 --> 01:01:51.528
That sort of a guru you need,

01:01:52.786 --> 01:01:54.786
who'll take you to hell!

01:02:00.079 --> 01:02:02.079
You don't want to go to heaven.

01:02:02.579 --> 01:02:05.850
You don't want to be the citizen of God's realm.

01:02:36.323 --> 01:02:37.752
Now whatever mantra you say,

01:02:39.838 --> 01:02:41.025
please listen.

01:02:42.653 --> 01:02:44.653
Put it in your heads what you are talking.

01:02:48.765 --> 01:02:51.709
What you are saying from your lips, listen.

01:02:52.843 --> 01:02:55.159
Put it in your heart what you are saying.

01:02:59.095 --> 01:03:00.453
Don't be hypocrites.

01:03:07.385 --> 01:03:08.966
No explanation is needed.

01:03:09.078 --> 01:03:12.242
"I've been to a guru, I've done this, I've done"- nothing of the kind.

01:03:16.002 --> 01:03:18.002
Even if at this stage, after so many days,

01:03:19.207 --> 01:03:22.284
if you have not realized that whatever we believe into

01:03:23.876 --> 01:03:24.958
should be

01:03:26.004 --> 01:03:27.484
part and parcel of ourselves.

01:03:27.737 --> 01:03:29.737
I mean these wretched people like

01:03:29.779 --> 01:03:31.672
Christians and other people, these

01:03:31.714 --> 01:03:33.486
Hindus and Muslims and all that,

01:03:33.581 --> 01:03:36.378
they've not seen God, they've not got realization, nothing

01:03:36.578 --> 01:03:38.806
but to them it becomes a faith, they fight for it.

01:03:40.117 --> 01:03:42.876
And for you people who have seen the reality - it is not,

01:03:44.187 --> 01:03:45.332
what's wrong with me?

01:03:57.250 --> 01:03:59.588
People are afraid of the police, afraid of this.

01:03:59.647 --> 01:04:01.647
You have entered into the Kingdom of God.

01:04:01.759 --> 01:04:03.042
You have seen what has happened

01:04:04.511 --> 01:04:07.350
with people who have tried to trouble me.

01:04:15.462 --> 01:04:16.530
Aren't you afraid of that?

01:04:28.131 --> 01:04:29.478
Don't become frivolous:

01:04:31.476 --> 01:04:34.315
"What was there to go to the airport, after all doesn't matter".

01:04:38.586 --> 01:04:40.712
All the Ganas went there, with me.

01:04:44.014 --> 01:04:46.278
They have all noted down, and they are here too.

01:04:50.866 --> 01:04:53.964
I am so cautiously taking you out, because you don't see them.

01:04:54.023 --> 01:04:55.777
But you'll see them very soon.

01:05:05.722 --> 01:05:08.340
It's not easy to control them also, you must know that.

01:05:09.897 --> 01:05:12.146
I do not control you, neither I control them.

01:05:21.897 --> 01:05:26.266
So now, I don't want to be unkind to people

01:05:26.661 --> 01:05:29.875
who have been desiring to come and see me, who love me so much.

01:05:31.397 --> 01:05:34.989
And I want to forgive you all, all of you,

01:05:35.894 --> 01:05:37.894
because this was the first mistake.

01:06:02.817 --> 01:06:05.346
Nobody should fix my program without asking me.

01:06:06.427 --> 01:06:07.938
Nobody should take such liberties.

01:06:08.614 --> 01:06:11.458
From next time I will not do anything of the kind,

01:06:11.464 --> 01:06:12.802
I'm telling you very clearly!

01:06:13.600 --> 01:06:15.600
You fix my program, and I'll let you down!

01:06:16.927 --> 01:06:19.275
Without asking me you are not to fix me anywhere.

01:06:23.893 --> 01:06:26.428
Without taking my permission, written permission.

01:06:28.516 --> 01:06:31.842
If you ever try to do such tricks with me, I'll put you right.

01:06:37.932 --> 01:06:41.398
You know I have all the powers to correct you.

01:06:45.437 --> 01:06:47.437
Don't take liberties with me anymore.

01:06:47.590 --> 01:06:49.156
I'm telling you, I am warning you.

01:06:52.699 --> 01:06:54.699
Try to understand, you are facing

01:06:56.042 --> 01:06:58.324
Someone, Who has all the Powers.

01:07:05.026 --> 01:07:05.787
You know that,

01:07:08.288 --> 01:07:11.009
know well, within yourself.

01:07:15.561 --> 01:07:19.356
It's not even like Mohammad. Mohammad just talked.

01:07:21.014 --> 01:07:22.334
He never gave realization,

01:07:24.881 --> 01:07:25.627
He warned.

01:07:27.368 --> 01:07:28.730
None of them, none of them.

01:07:30.834 --> 01:07:34.751
But after seeing, none of them have photographs as you have seen of mine.

01:07:34.830 --> 01:07:35.396
Have they?

01:07:44.466 --> 01:07:47.132
What more proof you want to know what I am.

01:07:49.003 --> 01:07:51.003
Now behave yourself. I'm warning you!

01:07:53.092 --> 01:07:53.868
Mahamaya -

01:07:57.032 --> 01:07:59.032
the other side of it is horrible.

01:08:00.591 --> 01:08:01.248
Be careful.

01:08:08.821 --> 01:08:09.917
Only for those

01:08:11.632 --> 01:08:13.632
who are my children I come on this earth.

01:08:14.584 --> 01:08:16.015
Not for those who are not,

01:08:18.244 --> 01:08:19.354
I've nothing to do with them.

01:08:27.457 --> 01:08:28.470
I did try

01:08:29.157 --> 01:08:31.235
to save you, as a prodigal son has to be saved,

01:08:31.330 --> 01:08:33.330
that's different. That's very different.

01:08:36.214 --> 01:08:39.532
But don't take liberties with me, I must tell you and warn you.

01:09:09.187 --> 01:09:11.168
I do not need any. The heat is just

01:09:12.369 --> 01:09:13.410
drying up everything.

01:09:29.636 --> 01:09:32.409
I feel like a Mother who is insulted, abused,

01:09:33.158 --> 01:09:35.158
ill-treated by her own children.

01:09:40.718 --> 01:09:42.430
You can take interest from others,

01:09:42.452 --> 01:09:44.559
not from your own children. You cannot.

01:09:44.953 --> 01:09:46.157
Very difficult.

01:09:54.453 --> 01:09:56.366
If you do not understand any protocol,

01:09:56.713 --> 01:09:57.944
because you are so naive,

01:09:58.329 --> 01:10:01.020
you have never known anything, you don't know how to respect.

01:10:05.595 --> 01:10:06.511
Then you better learn it.

01:10:15.180 --> 01:10:16.104
There is no Shraddha,

01:10:17.446 --> 01:10:20.359
because it was never there. You don't know how to respect anyone.

01:10:21.732 --> 01:10:24.456
You only have respect for yourself, perhaps may not be that even.

01:10:37.152 --> 01:10:41.829
Today is a day of a very great event.

01:10:45.448 --> 01:10:46.125
And

01:10:49.610 --> 01:10:54.235
“Guru" is a word as I told you, comes from the word "Gravity".

01:10:57.245 --> 01:11:00.187
The gravity. And the gravity,

01:11:01.326 --> 01:11:04.430
that's what I felt, that I have no gravity to attract you people.

01:11:06.504 --> 01:11:09.827
Or you people have no weight at all in you, that I should gravitate you.

01:11:18.452 --> 01:11:20.452
Anything that has weight

01:11:23.165 --> 01:11:26.736
gravitates, automatically.

01:11:29.479 --> 01:11:33.165
It does not gravitate towards itself, but it gravitates.

01:11:35.967 --> 01:11:39.609
There's also gravity between the matter.

01:11:42.753 --> 01:11:47.565
But what it has towards Mother Earth is incomparable.

01:11:49.521 --> 01:11:51.521
You throw any stone out, it comes back.

01:11:58.066 --> 01:12:00.066
Impossible to fight the gravity.

01:12:05.156 --> 01:12:09.560
And that gravity is the integration

01:12:10.327 --> 01:12:12.327
of your Shraddha,

01:12:13.659 --> 01:12:15.779
of your Dedication, and your surrender.

01:12:28.473 --> 01:12:33.544
Without that gravity you cannot nourish yourself, you cannot grow.

01:12:35.203 --> 01:12:37.203
Just imagine, the roots

01:12:39.307 --> 01:12:41.307
go towards the gravity.

01:12:43.099 --> 01:12:46.189
And when they are nourished, then only, the tree rises above.

01:12:48.664 --> 01:12:52.002
If your roots are not deep, if your roots are so flimsy,

01:12:52.784 --> 01:12:54.083
you cannot go down.

01:12:58.222 --> 01:13:00.852
Unless you go down in that gravity,

01:13:02.437 --> 01:13:03.286
you cannot come up.

01:13:05.078 --> 01:13:06.232
You cannot nourish yourself.

01:13:06.536 --> 01:13:08.757
Now my talk should not be a waste again.

01:13:09.257 --> 01:13:10.171
Please listen to me.

01:13:11.370 --> 01:13:14.227
I'm addressing to you, all of you. Remember that.

01:13:16.097 --> 01:13:19.320
Do not think that I'm addressing to somebody else. It is to you all.

01:13:22.085 --> 01:13:25.141
So the only way one can ascend in Sahaja Yoga is through

01:13:25.641 --> 01:13:26.511
putting the roots down.

01:13:27.402 --> 01:13:28.956
Allow the roots to grow.

01:13:30.574 --> 01:13:33.070
Unless and until roots grow, the tree cannot grow.

01:13:33.103 --> 01:13:36.103
I have seen many Sahaja yogis who talk big about Sahaja Yoga,

01:13:36.113 --> 01:13:38.576
they can write books, they can write things.

01:13:38.762 --> 01:13:41.964
The other day I saw somebody writing a big pamphlet about Sahaja Yoga,

01:13:43.008 --> 01:13:44.307
nothing inside the person!

01:13:49.765 --> 01:13:51.305
That's not the sign of a Sahaja yogi.

01:13:51.641 --> 01:13:54.196
A Sahaja yogi has to gravitate inside.

01:13:57.174 --> 01:13:58.001
How do we do it?

01:13:59.850 --> 01:14:05.094
In the year 1982 I told you the eightfold ways of doing it,

01:14:05.102 --> 01:14:06.604
and I said: I will tell you later.

01:14:07.888 --> 01:14:09.888
And I was about to tell you. But not now,

01:14:13.214 --> 01:14:16.069
there are other eight ways by which you can rise.

01:14:17.772 --> 01:14:21.992
Because, you are not yet grounded in Sahaja Yoga, you are not yet grounded.

01:14:27.997 --> 01:14:31.118
I thought you would be grounded, you're not.

01:14:33.569 --> 01:14:35.569
You have to nourish

01:14:37.691 --> 01:14:42.102
the other way around. The roots are in the head,

01:14:46.248 --> 01:14:52.345
by becoming thoughtless, by not making the cells to think.

01:14:55.744 --> 01:14:59.872
By resting them, by peace within. It is not a show of a peace,

01:15:00.518 --> 01:15:04.820
or just some people look very peaceful for a show.

01:15:05.630 --> 01:15:07.630
You have to work it out here in your head.

01:15:09.625 --> 01:15:11.625
The grounding - it has to go into your awareness.

01:15:15.115 --> 01:15:17.115
How? - Meditation.

01:15:19.584 --> 01:15:21.584
There's no discipline I'm told.

01:15:22.868 --> 01:15:25.362
Hounslow, I'm told, there's no discipline of any kind.

01:15:26.008 --> 01:15:28.210
I'm surprised Hounslow people have no discipline

01:15:28.382 --> 01:15:30.511
of getting up early in the morning and doing meditation.

01:15:36.626 --> 01:15:37.340
What are you doing?

01:15:40.757 --> 01:15:41.842
How are you going to grow?

01:15:45.514 --> 01:15:47.917
How does the tree grow? It does not grow in the day time.

01:15:49.128 --> 01:15:52.138
It grows in the morning, early in the morning, you never see that.

01:15:58.781 --> 01:16:01.153
How these roots are going to grow into the head?

01:16:02.018 --> 01:16:06.762
Into your brain, into that Jada (gross).

01:16:10.817 --> 01:16:14.365
You have to meditate. That's the only way you can do it.

01:16:14.628 --> 01:16:17.925
Those who do not meditate will become superficial.

01:16:19.245 --> 01:16:21.596
They'll not achieve anything, they create problems /?/.

01:16:22.479 --> 01:16:25.352
If they are right sided, they'll become supra-conscious, they'll become bhoots.

01:16:26.618 --> 01:16:29.329
If they are left-sided, they'll become left sided they will be thrown out!

01:16:29.370 --> 01:16:31.210
You've seen it, in the Sistine Chapel,

01:16:31.384 --> 01:16:33.628
you see Christ throwing them out one by one.

01:16:34.681 --> 01:16:38.129
And then you should not blame me. Just listening to me is not sufficient.

01:16:39.434 --> 01:16:43.716
It must grow. Actualization of the growth of the thing is needed.

01:16:43.855 --> 01:16:44.609
Do you follow that?

01:16:49.688 --> 01:16:52.824
You've read all kinds of nonsensical things before.

01:16:53.264 --> 01:16:55.553
All kinds of horrid things, I know what you have read.

01:16:57.664 --> 01:17:01.257
You have read in this horrible French country all kinds of

01:17:02.598 --> 01:17:03.905
sadists, like Sade,

01:17:07.350 --> 01:17:08.999
or Sade whatever you call him.

01:17:11.903 --> 01:17:13.148
And there were many like this,

01:17:14.360 --> 01:17:15.829
who wrote horrible books for you,

01:17:16.329 --> 01:17:18.329
which you have read. But they have not read "Advent".

01:17:18.829 --> 01:17:20.829
How many Sahaja yogis who have not yet read "Advent"?

01:17:22.403 --> 01:17:25.694
But only reading is not going to help, it must go into your brain.

01:17:26.710 --> 01:17:29.550
And brain means what? Into your Central Nervous System.

01:17:30.259 --> 01:17:32.259
Brain doesn't mean in the thinking.

01:17:32.982 --> 01:17:35.277
Into your central nervous system, into

01:17:36.740 --> 01:17:38.935
the cells of your central nervous system.

01:17:41.416 --> 01:17:43.416
That light has to come into the cells.

01:17:46.679 --> 01:17:48.679
You have to grow and grow, and grow!

01:17:54.077 --> 01:17:56.569
There's only way left out for you to go to Himalayas,

01:17:58.213 --> 01:18:00.213
and not to any Ashram or any place.

01:18:01.076 --> 01:18:03.410
But settle down somewhere where you don't eat anything

01:18:03.477 --> 01:18:06.570
or do anything, and take another birth. That's the only way I think.

01:18:13.726 --> 01:18:16.004
We can work it out, not difficult.

01:18:19.532 --> 01:18:21.532
If you have the seeking within your heart,

01:18:23.539 --> 01:18:24.928
and if you have understanding,

01:18:25.009 --> 01:18:26.953
sense, intelligence to understand that

01:18:26.965 --> 01:18:29.774
you have achieved something in life, you can do it.

01:18:33.190 --> 01:18:34.243
You all can do it.

01:18:38.971 --> 01:18:41.342
We don't forgive others, we forgive ourselves.

01:18:41.368 --> 01:18:42.859
This is the worst thing that we do.

01:18:44.810 --> 01:18:46.810
We all the time try to forgive others,

01:18:48.566 --> 01:18:49.612
that's the best way

01:18:52.359 --> 01:18:54.684
to work it out. But no, we try

01:18:56.119 --> 01:18:58.996
to forgive ourselves all the time and not to forgive others.

01:19:00.543 --> 01:19:02.543
Everything you do the other way around.

01:19:03.880 --> 01:19:08.608
We are Sahaja yogis. We're yogis, Saints.

01:19:11.675 --> 01:19:15.013
So, you have to be the guru.

01:19:18.094 --> 01:19:19.258
I'm a Guru myself,

01:19:20.456 --> 01:19:22.456
and what's the conveyance of a Guru?

01:19:23.975 --> 01:19:25.975
What is the animal he keeps? His dog.

01:19:28.805 --> 01:19:32.273
And do you know what a dog is? Do you know the qualities of a dog?

01:19:33.868 --> 01:19:35.696
He loves his master.

01:19:37.243 --> 01:19:38.878
He'll give his life for his Master.

01:19:41.290 --> 01:19:44.441
He'll not sleep till he sees his master return back.

01:19:50.062 --> 01:19:50.840
Any time!

01:19:53.084 --> 01:19:53.754
We had a dog,

01:19:55.063 --> 01:19:58.274
and every time I went out, every time

01:19:58.341 --> 01:20:01.467
he would come and sit at the door waiting for me.

01:20:08.651 --> 01:20:12.915
And some people tried very hard thing on him, some vegetarians

01:20:14.254 --> 01:20:17.767
and he was about to die. We put him in the hospital.

01:20:20.416 --> 01:20:22.416
When I went there, I sat before him.

01:20:22.693 --> 01:20:24.385
He just pulled all his body,

01:20:25.234 --> 01:20:29.100
put his head on my feet, and died peacefully.

01:20:29.687 --> 01:20:32.949
It's a dog, animal.

01:20:41.822 --> 01:20:44.142
When I went away, say, out of

01:20:45.340 --> 01:20:47.340
my house, he would not eat food till I came back.

01:20:48.063 --> 01:20:50.244
To any other country I went, he would not eat food

01:20:50.284 --> 01:20:52.284
for all these days. He would not eat his food,

01:20:52.672 --> 01:20:53.333
till I came back.

01:20:56.650 --> 01:20:59.579
He would not disturb me, but would sleep outside

01:21:00.404 --> 01:21:01.622
waiting for me to get up.

01:21:09.035 --> 01:21:12.171
That's a disciple. Unless and until you become good disciples

01:21:12.270 --> 01:21:13.653
how are you going to become the gurus?

01:21:15.374 --> 01:21:17.082
What's the use of my telling you anything about it?

01:21:18.094 --> 01:21:19.983
You don't have any discipline of your own,

01:21:20.030 --> 01:21:21.831
how are you going to give discipline to others?

01:21:23.331 --> 01:21:26.374
You yourself are tempted into all kinds of things,

01:21:27.059 --> 01:21:29.598
how are you going to make others

01:21:29.678 --> 01:21:31.864
understand you? What have you got, to become the guru?

01:21:33.057 --> 01:21:37.267
What can you give? All the Saints have spent their own money,

01:21:37.767 --> 01:21:40.020
all over the world any where it is.

01:21:42.305 --> 01:21:44.646
To spread Sahaja Yoga how much money have you spent?

01:21:47.305 --> 01:21:51.415
Of your own. How much money have you spent of your own to spread Sahaja Yoga?

01:21:57.359 --> 01:21:59.297
They used to starve themselves

01:21:59.579 --> 01:22:02.665
to get some. I have spent thousands, you know that very well.

01:22:02.859 --> 01:22:06.178
You know for definite how many thousands I have spent on you people.

01:22:08.193 --> 01:22:10.979
Even the Puja money that I get, you know, each and every money,

01:22:11.088 --> 01:22:14.039
I use it for buying some silver things for you.

01:22:15.125 --> 01:22:19.181
It should not be for you, it is for me I should say, but I do it.

01:22:26.409 --> 01:22:28.810
Every Saint used to spend money,

01:22:29.310 --> 01:22:32.693
Christ had to spend money to spread His Christianity,

01:22:32.926 --> 01:22:36.056
He never spread Christianity, His own message.

01:22:38.019 --> 01:22:39.273
Tukarama had to do it,

01:22:40.245 --> 01:22:42.245
Gyaneshwara had to do it. Whatever they had,

01:22:42.745 --> 01:22:45.523
they used that money, whatever they had, to spread

01:22:47.289 --> 01:22:51.008
Sahaja Yoga. Why? In Sahaja Yoga,

01:22:52.200 --> 01:22:54.847
the greatest thing I notice, everybody is so blessed.

01:22:56.684 --> 01:22:59.143
They have nice houses, nice ashrams,

01:22:59.281 --> 01:23:01.536
all conveniences, everything so well done.

01:23:03.609 --> 01:23:04.527
They are so blessed.

01:23:06.642 --> 01:23:09.979
God looks after them, all their problems get solved. They want

01:23:10.161 --> 01:23:13.129
marriages, so good marriages are done, everything is done well.

01:23:15.244 --> 01:23:17.244
Everything gets sorted out.

01:23:18.217 --> 01:23:20.062
Only blessings are there, no duties.

01:23:27.649 --> 01:23:29.485
How much money have you spent for Sahaja Yoga?

01:23:29.689 --> 01:23:31.538
First of all you should ask a question.

01:23:32.195 --> 01:23:33.864
How much time I have given for Sahaja Yoga?

01:23:34.759 --> 01:23:36.759
How many people I have given realization to?

01:23:39.315 --> 01:23:41.315
How much righteous and virtuous I have been?

01:23:44.091 --> 01:23:46.537
What have I done to bring the good name to Sahaja Yoga?

01:23:47.419 --> 01:23:49.673
What about my personal behavior, how I have lived?

01:23:58.423 --> 01:24:00.423
Arneau has spent lot of money I know,

01:24:02.253 --> 01:24:06.237
he and his wife. I know about everyone.

01:24:14.881 --> 01:24:16.881
You have to give time, money,

01:24:18.042 --> 01:24:20.042
everything, your job,

01:24:20.391 --> 01:24:22.969
everything you have to give up. People have given up jobs!

01:24:23.469 --> 01:24:25.469
I've told you the stories

01:24:26.306 --> 01:24:29.319
how people have sacrificed for ordinary things like

01:24:29.819 --> 01:24:31.819
freedom, fighting and all that.

01:24:36.499 --> 01:24:38.898
So today, as I told you, you have to resolve

01:24:39.398 --> 01:24:41.398
that we are going to have

01:24:42.693 --> 01:24:45.515
the growth within ourselves through our Shraddha

01:24:45.617 --> 01:24:46.827
and through our surrender.

01:24:47.884 --> 01:24:49.884
Only through Meditation you can do it.

